BeanDefinitionParser
public class JmsMessageDestinationBeanDefinitionParser
extends AbstractMessageDestinationBeanDefinitionParser

BeanDefinitionParser implementation for parsing the jms-message-destination element.

Configures the MessageDestinationFactory bean definition with the appropriate JmsAdapter class for connecting to JMS destinations.

Author:
Mark Fisher, Jeremy Grelle
